ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v25.message

Class RPI_I04

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractStructure
      • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractGroup
        • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractMessage
          • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v25.message.RPI_I04
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Group, Message, Structure, Visitable, Serializable

    public class RPI_I04
extends AbstractMessage

    Represents a RPI_I04 message structure (see chapter 11.3.4). This structure contains the following elements:

    • 1: MSH (Message Header)
    • 2: SFT (Software Segment) optional repeating
    • 3: MSA (Message Acknowledgment)
    • 4: RPI_I04_PROVIDER (a Group object) repeating
    • 5: PID (Patient Identification)
    • 6: NK1 (Next of Kin / Associated Parties) optional repeating
    • 7: RPI_I04_GUARANTOR_INSURANCE (a Group object) optional
    • 8: NTE (Notes and Comments) optional repeating
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
